				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>So, who&#8217;s up for Theme the next?</p>
<p>People seem to be having awesome, big, ideas for lots of the themes.<br />
Perhaps it&#8217;s time we started thinking about word limits.<br />
I&#8217;m very happy with the short form, but maybe we could do a longer story one in every four? Or a parallel project of sorts?<br />
Any thoughts, folks?</p>
