				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I am for a word limit mix up (but easy does it). Don&#8217;t think I am prepared to commit more time at the moment so a parallel project is not so good.</p>
<p>Options:<br />
a) 1 in 4 is 500-600 words normal fortnight submission<br />
b) 1 in 4 runs for double time (4 weeks) with 2 themes &#8211; 1 nano-fiction (&lt;50 words or the like) and the other longer  (say 500 words)</p>
<p>On the other hand this is a difficult thing we are doing, and if it ain&#039;t yet broke I&#039;m hesitate to fix it.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

